Text:
Any word on the quality of season 2?
All the season 2's I've tried to download are either in .mkv files or are of awful quality.
There are 2 srt files I noticed when I was already seeding. As to AVI files, they are OK http://img97.imageshack.us/img97/4233/57642274.jpg

Season 1 would not play for me at all. Tried VLC and MPC with K-Lite and CCCP.

Seasons 2-5 play fine, good quality.
Sound quality for me wasn't that good. Video quality was good though.
Audio quality for 2 is terrible, the video isn't very good either.  If anyone finds a good Season 2 please let me know, I've been looking.
Season 4 & 5 just don't work at all for me. An episode will play for a minute and then just freak out.. It's only with this download too,
